# Stage 7: Shared Sacrifice Ritual

label stage7_ritual_shared:
    scene bg garden with fade

    show h at left
    show l at center
    show y at right
    with dissolve

    h "Together, the burden is lighter."

    "Each person steps forward, offering a small piece of themselves."
    "A memory. A skill. A moment of joy."

    "The Echo receives these gifts, understanding the power of unity."

    "Echo" "You share freely what I was denied. Community. Connection."
    "Echo" "This is the greatest gift."

    "The portal opens, stable and clear."

    "Echo" "I go home. But I carry you with me. All of you."

    "The Echo departs. Each person forgets something small."
    "But together, they remember everything that matters."

    $ mystery_solved = True
    $ friends_saved = 5

    jump stage7_aftermath
